-28T11:29:04.23","modifiedByFull":"Heng, Rainer","remark":"included COFR expenses usd 566.25"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-06-07T15:25:45.537","modifiedByFull":"Fitzgerald, Ethan","remark":"Another straightforward PMI voyage which wrapped up the CVC voyages for Q1. Freight increased by $63k with an additional disport which also extended the voyage. The additional port also had an additional berth which is covered by the lumpsum of $20,500 for the port. This covers the higher port costs due to shifting/pilots/lines. We had a total of 17 days on demurrage at a rate of $42k, totaling about $730,000 in demurrage. \n\nAt the load port, there was an issue with the terminal using the wrong calculations and overloading the vessel by 800-900 bbls which had to be discharged back to shore before loading on top from a different shore tank. Thankfully this was an easy fix and the vessel only needed to discharge the qty back to shore before loading resumed. Following completion of loading, the charterers requested an internal transfer alongside which all costs were billed to charterers for the additional fuel and time. Bunker consumption increased due to the longer port stay at the discharge port as well as the IGS."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-05-30T16:22:57.04","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"FDA received for Veracruz."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-05-17T14:17:11.273","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Updated final demurrage"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-05-13T13:45:47.07","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Updated est demurrage"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-05-08T13:58:18.743","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Pajaritos Port costs more than generated"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-05-08T13:54:31.403","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Hou port costs updated"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-05-06T12:45:35.787","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Additional berth Veracruz"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-29T13:16:29.653","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Extended stay in Pajaritos. Est stay in Veracruz. Demur. included."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-24T15:37:06.963","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Extended stay in Pajaritos"},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-22T14:48:33.72","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Veracruz added as an additional port."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-19T17:08:03.327","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Hou time extended. Inc dem days."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-19T15:15:44.87","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Urea and CVE added from hire invoice."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-16T20:11:41.333","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"Vsl arrived earlier than estimated and saved bunkers as well."},{"modifiedDate":"2024-04-15T13:59:00.247","modifiedByFull":"Land, Macy","remark":"No cleaning as PMI agreed MTBE tanks are okay to load gasoline."}],"offhireList":[],"tcNumber":null,"tcOutIdEncrypted":null,"tcReletDetail":null}